author: Reuters Editorial
title: Czechs send facemasks to Italy after mix-up over Chinese gift
description: The Czech Republic sent 110,000 facemasks to Italy on Monday after confusion around a larger shipment of gear to protect against the new coronavirus was impounded by Czech authorities last week.
content:
PRAGUE (Reuters) - The Czech Republic sent 110,000 facemasks to Italy on Monday after confusion around a larger shipment of gear to protect against the new coronavirus was impounded by Czech authorities last week.
